snippet.title: Amber Heard Denied Court Settlements
snippet.description:
Information regarding Amber Heard's legal requests and allegations against Johnny Depp have surfaced.

The actress was granted a domestic violence restraining order against her soon-to-be ex-husband after alleging abuse and showing up to a Los Angeles courtroom visibly bruised in the face.
And now it seems Ambers requests of court settlements have been denied, including 50 thousand dollars spousal support.
Up until now, there have been testimonies of eye witnesses including the couples neighbours who have heard and seen Johnnys physical abuse towards Amber. 
Tune in for more on momoviez.
